<tt xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml" xmlns:amll="http://www.example.com/ns/amll" xmlns:itunes="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal" xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" xmlns:tts="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#styling" itunes:timing="Word" xml:lang="ja"><head><metadata><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v1"/><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v2"><ttm:name type="full">girl</ttm:name></ttm:agent><ttm:agent type="person" xml:id="v3"><ttm:name type="full">woman</ttm:name></ttm:agent><amll:meta key="musicName" value="恋人を射ち堕とした日"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="恋人射杀的那一天"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="射杀恋人之日"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="Koibito wo Uchiotoshita Hi"/><amll:meta key="musicName" value="射杀恋人的那天"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="Sound Horizon"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="サウンドホライズン"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="幻想乐团"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="幻想楽団"/><amll:meta key="artists" value="SH"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Elysion -楽園への前奏曲-"/><amll:meta key="album" value="Elysion -Rakuen eno Zensoukyoku-"/><amll:meta key="ncmMusicId" value="22782041"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="002LE8A13P0ODB"/><amll:meta key="qqMusicId" value="1798440"/><amll:meta key="spotifyId" value="3R5dlgYzG793fcY6niY0ES"/><amll:meta key="appleMusicId" value="1516976301"/><amll:meta key="isrc" value="JPKI00400346"/><amll:meta key="作曲" value="Revo"/><amll:meta key="作词" value="Revo"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithub" value="68000793"/><amll:meta key="ttmlAuthorGithubLogin" value="ranhengzhang"/><iTunesMetadata xmlns="http://music.apple.com/lyric-ttml-internal"><translations><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="en"><text for="L1">The bowstring strains, bursting flame that freezes the night sky</text><text for="L2">A cold blue elegy of parting, shooting down the lover...</text><text for="L3">A thing forgotten from distant days, the scars left torn asunder</text><text for="L4">The accursed vow harbored deep within that heart</text><text for="L5">&quot;The inescapable ending — at least let it come by your beloved hand...&quot;</text><text for="L6">The darkness of irresistible impulse enveloped him...</text><text for="L7">A warped world, spiral flames piercing through the cycle of rebirth</text><text for="L8">A cold crimson kiss stained with blood, shooting down the lover...</text><text for="L9">Is there nothing you have left behind...?</text><text for="L10">In an ancient legend: one who is wounded by that demon</text><text for="L11">The curse courses through their entire body</text><text for="L12">And before long shall become the very same demon...</text><text for="L13">When was that wound inflicted?</text><text for="L14">It traces back to the day the two first met</text><text for="L15">The wound he sustained when he saved her</text><text for="L16">Everything had begun from the moment they met...</text><text for="L17">Their meeting was a promise of loss...</text><text for="L18">Tears long withered harbor a sorrowful blue flame</text><text for="L19">Loosing an arrow that gleams with silver light</text><text for="L20">Again and again, only... until he draws his final breath...</text><text for="L21">In a world that has lost its beloved one <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(Why...)</span></text><text for="L22">What color flowers shall ever bloom?</text><text for="L23">A cruciform flame embracing the moon, wound endlessly with briars</text><text for="L24">A cold white arrow of the final hour, shooting me down...</text><text for="L25">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text><text for="L26">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text><text for="L27">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text><text for="L28">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text><text for="L29">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text><text for="L30">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text><text for="L31">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text><text for="L32">In a world that has lost its beloved one, what color flowers shall bloom...</text></translation><translation type="subtitle" xml:lang="zh-Hans"><text for="L1">长弓震颤 迸裂的焰火 将夜空凝结</text><text for="L2">凛然苍蓝的诀别之诗 将身为恋人的你射杀……</text><text for="L3">遥远之日的遗留之物 被撕裂的道道伤痕</text><text for="L4">将受诅咒的约定 刻入那胸膛之中</text><text for="L5">「无法逃避的结局 至少由那心爱之人亲手……」</text><text for="L6">无法抗拒的疯狂冲动 将他笼罩吞噬……</text><text for="L7">扭曲世界的螺旋之焰 贯穿轮回往复</text><text for="L8">凛然绯红的血濡之吻 将身为恋人的你射杀……</text><text for="L9">还有什么忘记了吗？……</text><text for="L10">古老的传说中 被那魔物所伤之人</text><text for="L11">诅咒将于全身游走奔涌</text><text for="L12">终有一日 会化作同样的魔物吧…</text><text for="L13">那伤痕又是什么时候留下的？</text><text for="L14">那要追溯至二人相遇的那一天</text><text for="L15">那是他为救她时所受的伤</text><text for="L16">一切自相遇之时 便已悄然开始……</text><text for="L17">相遇即是通往相离的约定……</text><text for="L18">干涸殆尽的泪水 宿有悲伤的苍蓝之焰</text><text for="L19">射出闪耀银色光辉的箭矢</text><text for="L20">无论多少次 直至……他气绝而亡……</text><text for="L21">在失去所爱之人的世界里 <span xmlns:ttm="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml#metadata" ttm:role="x-bg" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">(怎么会……)</span></text><text for="L22">会绽放何种色彩的花呢？</text><text for="L23">环抱月华的十字之焰 荆棘缠绕不倦</text><text for="L24">凛然纯白的临终箭矢 将身为恋人的我射杀……</text><text for="L25">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text><text for="L26">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text><text for="L27">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text><text for="L28">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text><text for="L29">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text><text for="L30">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text><text for="L31">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text><text for="L32">在失去所爱之人的世界里 会绽放何种色彩的花……</text></translation></translations><songwriters><songwriter>Revo</songwriter></songwriters><transliterations><transliteration xml:lang="ja-Latn"><text for="L1"><span begin="2.270" end="2.740" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">yu mi</span> <span begin="2.740" end="3.170" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ga</span> <span begin="3.170" end="3.470" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">shi</span> <span begin="3.470" end="3.750" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">na</span> <span begin="3.750" end="4.070" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ri</span> <span begin="4.070" end="4.720" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ha ji</span> <span begin="4.720" end="4.960" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ke</span> <span begin="4.960" end="5.200" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ta</span> <span begin="5.200" end="5.880" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ho no o</span> <span begin="6.160" end="6.420" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">yo</span> <span begin="6.420" end="7.060" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">zo ra</span> <span begin="7.060" end="7.410" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">o</span> <span begin="7.410" end="8.060" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ko o</span> <span begin="8.060" end="8.330" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ra</span> <span begin="8.330" end="8.660" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">se</span> <span begin="8.660" end="9.790" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">te</span></text><text for="L2"><span begin="10.130" end="10.630" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">rin</span> <span begin="10.630" end="11.090" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">to</span> <span begin="11.090" end="11.640" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">a o</span> <span begin="11.640" end="12.020" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">ku</span> <span begin="12.020" end="12.620" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">wa ka</span> <span begin="12.620" end="12.850" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">re</span> <span begin="12.850" end="13.100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">no</span> <span begin="13.100" end="13.490" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">u ta</span> <span begin="13.490" end="13.740" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">o</span> <span begin="14.080" end="14.910" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/ns/ttml">a na ta</span> 